  "title": "Student Care Teacher (Full-Time)",
  "description": "<p>Roles and Responsibilities</p>\n<p>- Supervise and guide students with their homework.</p>\n<p>- Involved with classroom management, maintain order in classroom and during outdoor activities.</p>\n<p>- Plan, execute, organise learning resources/activities.</p>\n<p>- Assist to implement creative ideas, activities and lesson plans.</p>\n<p>- Ensure the safety and wellbeing of the students.</p>\n<p>- Work with the Centre Supervisor.</p>\n<p>- Fetching students from nearby schools.</p>\n<p>- Sanitise and maintain classrooms and centre's environment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Requirements :</p>\n<p>- Minumun N/O Level, NITEC or its equivalent</p>\n<p>- Bilingual in English and Chinese</p>\n<p>- Patient and love in nurturing children</p>\n<p>- Able to guide in primary school subjetcs</p>\n<p>- Working hours - 7 hours daily during school terms (12-7pm) and 8 hours daily during school holidays and ad hoc school closures.</p>\n<p>- Working location : - Near MRT and LRT stations</p>",
